body:
Champion quotes can be pretty great in this game. But there are several that could get really awkward when said in the wrong setting. Name below some that you would *not* want to hear your doctor say.

Examples:
{{champion:8}} &quot;The clot thickens.&quot;

{{champion:31}} &quot;You are such... hideous creatures!&quot;

{{champion:161}} &quot;To date, none have survived preliminary testing.&quot;

{{champion:119}} &quot;Seems to be blood everywhere I go.&quot;

{{champion:59}}  &quot;Today is a good day to die!&quot;
